      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAKEVIEW CHASER (1) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish half a length back in second (22.91) at Warragul in a Maiden over 400m. Leading chance again. FIRE RATED (6) is a first starter by Feral Franky out of Zara Marnie with no trial form to work with. Betting to provide the best guide to his chances. FULL BORE LISA (2) has an honest record despite remaining a maiden and is long overdue for a win, having placed five of eight career runs. Gave a big sight last time racing on speed much of the way. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to feature. MISS RODRIGO (3) is a newcomer from the Justin Bowman kennel. Expected to produce a bold debut.",
